news.title: Cera Sanitaryware's net profit up 31.91% in Q3 FY23
news.para: Cera Sanitaryware's net consolidated income stood at Rs 471.06 crore in Q3 FY23, a growth of 20.06 per cent from Rs 392.35 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Aptus Value Housing Finance's net profit up 23.74% in Q3 FY23
news.para: Aptus Value Housing Finance's net consolidated income stood at Rs 294.80 crore in Q3 FY23, a dip of 36.39 per cent from Rs 216.31 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Godrej Properties' net profit up 44.54% in Q3 FY23
news.para: Godrej Properties' net consolidated income stood at Rs 404.58 crore in Q3 FY23, a dip of 13.35 per cent from Rs 466.91 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.
